* Update version in php_var_representation.h to remove dev suffix.
* Update version, release date in package.xml.
* Run `phpize; ./configure; make clean test`.
* Run `pecl package package.xml`.
* Run `pecl install var_representation-XXX.tgz`.
* Commit.
* Create a release.
* Bump version in php_var_representation.h and add dev suffix.
* Copy release in package.xml into changelog.
* Clear current changelog, bump versions and add dev suffix.
* Commit.
* Upload package on pecl.php.net.
